PIZZA PIZZA.

175
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,554
(RISO)

176
00:07:50,637 --> 00:07:54,391
JESSE STEFANOVICH,
O ÚLTIMO DOS GRANDES GASTADORES.

177
00:07:54,474 --> 00:07:55,684
EI,
EU SOU ASSIM.

178
00:07:58,979 --> 00:08:00,814
ELLIE:
NOSSA... (RISO)

179
00:08:00,898 --> 00:08:01,899
QUER DIZER... NOSSA!

180
00:08:05,068 --> 00:08:05,944
MUITO ARTICULADA.

181
00:08:06,028 --> 00:08:06,904
POSSO TE CITAR?

182
00:08:09,031 --> 00:08:10,324
ALGO MAIS A DIZER?

183
00:08:10,407 --> 00:08:13,660
